lead_paragraph: Kelsey Plum had 26 points, Natalie Romeo hit seven 3-pointers for 21 points and No. 15 Washington rolled to an 83-53 win over Portland on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Plum, Romero Lead No. 15 Washington Women Past Portland
